About
Artfol is an independent social media platform focused on providing a safe and positive space for artists to engage with their community and other artists! We are a small team of passionate individuals who launched Artfol publicly in 2021 and are constantly working on adding more features to help artists share their work online.
One of our main goals is to create a supportive and inclusive community for artists of all backgrounds and skill levels. As such, any and all forms of visual art are welcome on Artfol, including painting, photography, sculpture, and digital art. Whether you're a seasoned professional or just starting out, we believe that everyone deserves a platform to share their creative expression.
Artfol is designed to empower artists to showcase their work in their own unique way. We believe that every artist should have the freedom to show off their creativity, and our platform provides the tools to do just that. From choosing a profile theme to currating your gallery and creating custom collections, Artfol strives to provide a user-friendly experience that allows artists to focus on what they do best â€“ creating.
In addition to the customization options, we offer a many unique features that are focused on promoting engagement and community interaction. From participating in community challenges to resharing your favorite art and creating collections, there's always something fun to do on Artfol!
We believe that art should be accessible to everyone, which is why our platform is free to use and open to all. Create an account and Our mission is to foster a supportive and inclusive community that celebrates creativity and encourages artists to pursue their passions.
